00:25:13.060 --> 00:25:17.010 align:middle line:84%
There's an attitude in Alaska
that if you go to an Ivy League

00:25:17.010 --> 00:25:19.610 align:middle line:90%
school, you need to overcome it.

00:25:19.610 --> 00:25:24.500 align:middle line:84%
So I don't come to you
as I'm from Harvard.

00:25:24.500 --> 00:25:26.770 align:middle line:90%
I have some modesty around this.

00:25:26.770 --> 00:25:27.890 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Interesting.

00:25:27.890 --> 00:25:28.170 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:25:28.170 --> 00:25:30.370 align:middle line:84%
You were just talking about
muffin tops a little bit ago.

00:25:30.370 --> 00:25:30.890 align:middle line:90%
>>GOTTFRIED: Yes, muffin tops.

00:25:30.890 --> 00:25:33.390 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Now, when we were
talking about this cycle of

00:25:33.390 --> 00:25:36.560 align:middle line:84%
stressed out female
hormones, and some

00:25:36.560 --> 00:25:38.090 align:middle line:84%
of the primary
players-- and we're

00:25:38.090 --> 00:25:41.930 align:middle line:84%
going to go into a couple of
them in more detail in a bit.

00:25:41.930 --> 00:25:44.312 align:middle line:84%
But there's also a
psychological factor.

00:25:44.312 --> 00:25:45.020 align:middle line:90%
>>GOTTFRIED: Yes.

00:25:45.020 --> 00:25:50.170 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And that is when
your great-grandmother hit

00:25:50.170 --> 00:25:53.470 align:middle line:84%
her 50s, 60s, and 70s,
she wasn't expecting

00:25:53.470 --> 00:25:57.210 align:middle line:84%
to look like she did in her
