00:25:57.210 --> 00:25:58.610 align:middle line:90%
>>GOTTFRIED: Yes.

00:25:58.610 --> 00:26:00.530 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Are we
totally delusional?

00:26:00.530 --> 00:26:04.680 align:middle line:84%
