00:26:10.570 --> 00:26:12.270 align:middle line:84%
What's going on here
psychologically,

00:26:12.270 --> 00:26:14.936 align:middle line:84%
and how much of this do you have
to deal with with your clients?

00:26:14.936 --> 00:26:17.844 align:middle line:90%
Just their own self-perception.

00:26:17.844 --> 00:26:19.260 align:middle line:84%
>>GOTTFRIED: Well,
in some ways, I

00:26:19.260 --> 00:26:23.040 align:middle line:84%
