society to hold us back anymore

00:26:23.040 --> 00:26:25.690 align:middle line:90%
because we do it to ourselves.

00:26:25.690 --> 00:26:28.280 align:middle line:84%
And we're surrounded by all
of these images and media--

00:26:28.280 --> 00:26:33.330 align:middle line:84%
everyone knows this-- of
the ideal of the female form

00:26:33.330 --> 00:26:37.104 align:middle line:84%
being what I would call
an anorexic adolescent.

00:26:37.104 --> 00:26:38.520 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: 6 feet
tall, 115 pounds.

00:26:38.520 --> 00:26:40.980 align:middle line:84%
>>GOTTFRIED: 6 feet tall, a
freak of nature, honestly.

00:26:40.980 --> 00:26:42.375 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: A genetic mutation.

00:26:42.375 --> 00:26:43.750 align:middle line:84%
>>GOTTFRIED: So
someone who's got

00:26:43.750 --> 00:26:48.170 align:middle line:84%
