00:27:25.460 --> 00:27:27.230 align:middle line:84%
She didn't have a
muffin top because I

00:27:27.230 --> 00:27:29.740 align:middle line:84%
think her cortisol was right
in that Goldilocks position--

00:27:29.740 --> 00:27:31.440 align:middle line:90%
