00:27:38.790 --> 00:27:39.790 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:27:39.790 --> 00:27:41.270 align:middle line:84%
That's a really
big one, the damage

00:27:41.270 --> 00:27:44.940 align:middle line:84%
