of women to try

00:27:44.940 --> 00:27:47.290 align:middle line:84%
to attain this thing that's
really unattainable by way

00:27:47.290 --> 00:27:50.800 align:middle line:84%
of imagery, by what's put
out by Madison Avenue.

00:27:50.800 --> 00:27:52.610 align:middle line:84%
I know very few
women they don't have

00:27:52.610 --> 00:27:55.840 align:middle line:84%
a fair amount of self-loathing
about their bodies,

00:27:55.840 --> 00:27:57.494 align:middle line:84%
and some of them
