00:27:57.494 --> 00:27:58.660 align:middle line:90%
>>GOTTFRIED: It's very true.

00:27:58.660 --> 00:28:03.690 align:middle line:84%
There's a disconnect
between who we are

00:28:03.690 --> 00:28:07.570 align:middle line:90%
and who we feel we should be.

00:28:07.570 --> 00:28:10.320 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And let me
ask you then on that.

00:28:10.320 --> 00:28:13.650 align:middle line:84%
If you were to go back to an
era and look at Hollywood--

00:28:13.650 --> 00:28:16.990 align:middle line:84%
let's say Hollywood maybe
in a purer sense, where

00:28:16.990 --> 00:28:20.090 align:middle line:84%
you have people from the
town and community, and even

00:28:20.090 --> 00:28:22.030 align:middle line:90%
Aunt Bea thrown in there.

00:28:22.030 --> 00:28:25.340 align:middle line:84%
If you looked at women
from another time,

00:28:25.340 --> 00:28:29.210 align:middle line:84%
where would you say a
standard healthy female form

00:28:29.210 --> 00:28:30.326 align:middle line:90%
actually existed?

00:28:30.326 --> 00:28:34.022 align:middle line:90%


00:28:34.022 --> 00:28:35.980 align:middle line:84%
Because I know there's
no standard among women,

00:28:35.980 --> 00:28:38.210 align:middle line:84%
but what era would
we look to where

00:28:38.210 --> 00:28:41.039 align:middle line:84%
that's natural-- some
people worked on the farm,

00:28:41.039 --> 00:28:43.330 align:middle line:84%
some people have to walk
because they didn't have cars.

00:28:43.330 --> 00:28:46.760 align:middle line:84%
It was just a more
organic kind of lifestyle,

00:28:46.760 --> 00:28:49.430 align:middle line:84%
but not necessarily focused on
oh, I've got to lose weight.

00:28:49.430 --> 00:28:50.180 align:middle line:90%
>>GOTTFRIED: Sure.

00:28:50.180 --> 00:28:52.590 align:middle line:84%
Well, you know,
there's-- we've gone--

00:28:52.590 --> 00:28:54.340 align:middle line:84%
the pendulum swings
back and forth, right?

00:28:54.340 --> 00:28:54.570 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:28:54.570 --> 00:28:56.986 align:middle line:84%
>>GOTTFRIED: You can think of
the flappers in the '20s who

00:28:56.986 --> 00:28:58.580 align:middle line:84%
