00:28:58.580 --> 00:29:01.340 align:middle line:90%
and had almost no estrogen.

00:29:01.340 --> 00:29:03.092 align:middle line:84%
I don't think that's
the healthiest form.

00:29:03.092 --> 00:29:05.550 align:middle line:84%
I also think Twiggy in the '60s
is not the healthiest form.

00:29:05.550 --> 00:29:06.420 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, it
was not healthy.

00:29:06.420 --> 00:29:07.711 align:middle line:90%
>>GOTTFRIED: So it's not those.

00:29:07.711 --> 00:29:09.610 align:middle line:84%
I'll start with the
