00:29:28.590 --> 00:29:30.170 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah, absolutely.

00:29:30.170 --> 00:29:31.370 align:middle line:84%
>>GOTTFRIED: Doesn't that
sound like a great tribe?

00:29:31.370 --> 00:29:31.995 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:29:31.995 --> 00:29:34.840 align:middle line:84%
>>GOTTFRIED: But to get to
your question about Hollywood

00:29:34.840 --> 00:29:36.070 align:middle line:90%
and what's healthy.

00:29:36.070 --> 00:29:37.980 align:middle line:84%
When I think about
the Victorian era,

00:29:37.980 --> 00:29:44.074 align:middle line:84%
when I think about
the form of women

00:29:44.074 --> 00:29:48.142 align:middle line:84%
when it was valued for them
to have more fat on them,

00:29:48.142 --> 00:29:50.100 align:middle line:84%
I don't necessarily think
that that was so good

00:29:50.100 --> 00:29:53.360 align:middle line:84%
either because many of those
