would stay feminine forever

00:33:37.925 --> 00:33:40.930 align:middle line:84%
and young forever if they
took this prescription.

00:33:40.930 --> 00:33:45.020 align:middle line:84%
And oh, by the way, it causes
endometrial cancer, cancer

00:33:45.020 --> 00:33:47.110 align:middle line:84%
of the uterus, cancer
of the breasts,

00:33:47.110 --> 00:33:49.100 align:middle line:84%
increases your risk
of heart disease.

00:33:49.100 --> 00:33:52.610 align:middle line:84%
And we didn't know that until
we did the best type of study,

00:33:52.610 --> 00:33:53.970 align:middle line:90%
which is a randomized trial.

00:33:53.970 --> 00:33:57.000 align:middle line:84%
And that was not
done until 1999.

00:33:57.000 --> 00:33:59.970 align:middle line:84%
The next study was done in
2002, which most people know

00:33:59.970 --> 00:34:01.970 align:middle line:84%
about the Women's
Health Initiative.

00:34:01.970 --> 00:34:05.810 align:middle line:84%
But 57 years of a vast,
uncontrolled medical experiment

00:34:05.810 --> 00:34:06.960 align:middle line:90%
on women.

00:34:06.960 --> 00:34:08.690 align:middle line:90%
And that's shameful.

00:34:08.690 --> 00:34:12.690 align:middle line:84%
I was part of the conventional
medical training that was not

00:34:12.690 --> 00:34:16.284 align:middle line:84%
just suggesting
conventional hormone

00:34:16.284 --> 00:34:18.159 align:middle line:84%
therapy, synthetic
hormone therapy, to women,

00:34:18.159 --> 00:34:20.820 align:middle line:90%
but proselytizing.

00:34:20.820 --> 00:34:25.830 align:middle line:84%
So I really feel like
we've got a high bar now

00:34:25.830 --> 00:34:28.840 align:middle line:84%
in medicine to keep
women safe when

00:34:28.840 --> 00:34:31.000 align:middle line:90%
it comes to these interventions.

00:34:31.000 --> 00:34:34.010 align:middle line:84%
So let's get to some
of those interventions.

00:34:34.010 --> 00:34:36.239 align:middle line:84%
When it comes to your fork,
we'll start with that.

00:34:36.239 --> 00:34:38.469 align:middle line:84%
Maybe how you eat, move,
think, and supplement.

