dairy, especially

00:34:46.280 --> 00:34:48.010 align:middle line:90%
conventional cow dairy.

00:34:48.010 --> 00:34:48.639 align:middle line:90%
Not organic.

00:34:48.639 --> 00:34:50.055 align:middle line:84%
>>GOTTFRIED: Not
raw, necessarily.

00:34:50.055 --> 00:34:50.380 align:middle line:84%
It seems to have a
different spectrum.

00:34:50.380 --> 00:34:52.120 align:middle line:84%
>>GOTTFRIED: Not
raw necessarily.

00:34:52.120 --> 00:34:53.570 align:middle line:90%
It's a different spectrum.

00:34:53.570 --> 00:34:58.040 align:middle line:84%
When it comes from
goats and sheep,

00:34:58.040 --> 00:35:00.380 align:middle line:84%
that's better, less
allergenic, less likely

00:35:00.380 --> 00:35:02.410 align:middle line:84%
to create a bad
neighborhood in your body.

00:35:02.410 --> 00:35:05.290 align:middle line:84%
It's all about if we look at
personalized medicine, which

00:35:05.290 --> 00:35:07.040 align:middle line:84%
