Right now it costs
about $10,000.

00:35:16.330 --> 00:35:17.746 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah,
that is very cool.

00:35:17.746 --> 00:35:19.460 align:middle line:84%
>>GOTTFRIED: And
the interesting part

00:35:19.460 --> 00:35:25.180 align:middle line:84%
