construct your life.

00:35:29.060 --> 00:35:31.580 align:middle line:84%
It's the supplements you
take, it's the amount of sleep

00:35:31.580 --> 00:35:33.030 align:middle line:90%
that you have.

00:35:33.030 --> 00:35:36.220 align:middle line:84%
50 to 80% of how
your DNA is expressed

00:35:36.220 --> 00:35:38.710 align:middle line:84%
is based on those four factors,
how you eat, move, think,

00:35:38.710 --> 00:35:39.720 align:middle line:90%
and supplement.

00:35:39.720 --> 00:35:41.444 align:middle line:84%
So that's an
incredible opportunity.

00:35:41.444 --> 00:35:42.110 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It is.

00:35:42.110 --> 00:35:44.100 align:middle line:84%
The field of epigenetics
is really growing fast.

00:35:44.100 --> 00:35:44.380 align:middle line:90%
>>GOTTFRIED: So cool.

